Title: Journey of poor
DateModified: '2018-02-21'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/journey-of-poor
SetInCountry: India
Category: A decision that pushed me to the edge
AuthorName: Shyam Kumar
AuthorCountry: India
Text: "A story of poor boy. \n     \n     The boy he's name is shyam  when he was\
  \ born he didn't see his parents then he grow up with his grandmother\u200B. Once\
  \ the old lady saw that boy then suddenly he called him and tell the truth of his\
  \ born and he shocked and whipped and crying a lot.  Then he had a one wish that\
  \ wish was once in  a life see his parents face but unlucky he can't\u200B see his\u200B\
  \ parents . He is very sad .  Then he leaving and started him own business suddenly\
  \ he got one bad news then he go and told his grandmother and  both are crying a\
  \ lot.  What was that news really it's very sad he got news that is his parents\
  \ dead."
